暂存：<code>git add .gitattributes</code></li>\r\n 	<li>提交：<code>git commit -m "Add a .gitattributes file</code></li>\r\n 	<li>接下来上传到Ubuntu上，<code>.gitattributes</code>就发挥了作用。使用<code>git status</code>查看，整个工作区都清静了。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>', '消除Git diff中^M的差异', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-22 21:32:27', '2016-10-22 13:32:27', '', 40, 'http://localhost:8001/?p=114', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
